description:
Episode 239 - Happy Wednesday! Coming at you is a great conversation that I had with Jake Ewald from Modern Baseball/Slaughter Beach, Dog about SO many things including religion, how Modern Baseball has grown and metal-core. It was quite an in depth and introspective conversation that surprised me in many places, so I hope it does the same for you.
